Say '''Lavezares''' et kumapat ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Northern Samar]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 27,464 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 119.5 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6404.	
															
